hone X 得Apple就唔駛保養?"},{"pid":"ee153dbba4e7df5a249ce14fbfafbe64b180867f","tid":417671,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T04:48:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用木地板就最on9 不過今時今日冇所謂喇 冇人理架喇 要黎炒姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n手工差就咩都差<br />\n<br />\n好像石質地板<br />\n<br />\n手工差  冬天成個地下爆起"},{"pid":"a1b085ca13342cdb257b6bf9697e39f19291b020","tid":417671,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T04:49:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"07a8a8aa81758debb067ddf500d7292ae5f6b271","tid":417671,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T04:51:01.000Z","msg":"4千萬3千呎獨立屋都買到啦"},{"pid":"43eeb6f0f88d09347f81929eeab7ca5841f299b1","tid":417671,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T04:51:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"51d10af610d05430a3cdb43ed508a4d7e995d5ae","tid":417671,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T05:00:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4千萬3千呎獨立屋都買到啦</blockquote><br />\n2000呎特色戶先賣到咁貴<br />\n另外迎海出名潮濕仲用木地板"},{"pid":"4bc078ec306ac21d861fd75fbe1c4bf3c4dd9d8d","tid":417671,"uid":98221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T05:31:41.000Z","msg":"用四千幾萬不如住比華利山仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b1e22a14144d97dd0486706a5454e11da884223","tid":417671,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T05:44:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>4千萬3千呎獨立屋都買到啦</blockquote><br />\n2000呎特色戶先賣到咁貴<br />\n另外迎海出名潮濕仲用木地板</blockquote><br />\n搭單問下，木地板真係咁差？香港一直都好潮濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果真係用有啲咩要注意？黎緊裝修想用木地板"},{"pid":"1ab95dfc5fc37a3ece820c44b05fcbde97c408d5","tid":417671,"uid":51072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T05:52:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用四千幾萬不如住比華利山仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></bl